{
  "stem": "444.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he had with him his wife, his mother, two daughters, and, I believe, his mother-in-law.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they all survived.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then I knew of other Jewish families in that little town, and they all survived.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Nobody denounced them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, there was the famous opera singer, Maria Modrakowfska who was later a wife of a Polish ambassador to Belgium.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were hiding up in that little town, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I spoke to about her about Jews.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I got a letter from her son, who's a professor of university in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He wrote to me about his father.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And his father was a-- rather a friend of Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Because at the meeting of the Polish Underground, somebody said about what he did to the Jews, throwing somebody's table.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he gave him a speech and told him that thanks to people like you, we have a bad name in the world.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there were people that they all knew.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I found out from his son that his mother was speaking to the mayor.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had-- one evening, they had something to drink, and they knew about every Jew in that town that we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, some people thought that I was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Morgan-- Morgans thought that I was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "His wife thought that I was not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My wife was Jewish, so anyhow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we were speaking of each other, but we never mentioned to each other.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because you say something to someone and he get arrested, and you in, see?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we never spoke to-- to-- we knew Jews that we never admitted that we are Jewish or we know that you are Jewish.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That was the way to-- to-- to survive, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
